      out.write("    horarios:'🕐 **Attendance schedules:**\\n\\n📅 Monday to Friday\\n🕖 Morning: 7:00 AM – 12:00 PM\\n🕑 Afternoon: 2:00 PM – 5:00 PM\\n\\n_For a specific doctor\\'s schedule, check the **Schedules** section._',\n");
